          <div class="interpretation-card" style="padding: 12px; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 6px;">
            <strong style="color: var(--primary);">Interpretation C: The Political Realist (The Post-Tet View)</strong>
            <blockquote style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-style: italic; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95em;">"The Tet Offensive revealed the patience and durability of the enemy. It convinced many that the cost of winning was out of proportion to U.S. interests. We realized we could not do what we wished to do because the enemy could replenish its manpower so easily, matching every escalation we made."</blockquote>
          </div>
